a lot of complexity.

00:24:41.530 --> 00:24:43.010
It's a huge amount
of complexity,

00:24:43.010 --> 00:24:44.968
but it's really important
that we pay attention

00:24:44.968 --> 00:24:48.360
to this complexity so that you
as developers and designers

00:24:48.360 --> 00:24:50.824
