00:25:26.670 --> 00:25:28.464
And they're doing
this because they

00:25:28.464 --> 00:25:29.630
want to leapfrog each other.

00:25:29.630 --> 00:25:31.170
They want to say,
we are this brand

00:25:31.170 --> 00:25:33.030
and this is our characteristics.

00:25:33.030 --> 00:25:36.240
And our system
basically owes them

00:25:36.240 --> 00:25:38.470
to adapt and integrate
well with that system

00:25:38.470 --> 00:25:41.490
