as apps and services are

00:25:48.800 --> 00:25:53.210
concerned, so you didn't have
to be an automotive expert.

00:25:53.210 --> 00:25:55.220
And one of the other
interesting challenges

00:25:55.220 --> 00:25:57.790
is that as an ecosystem, of
course, we're in many countries

00:25:57.790 --> 00:26:01.100
and Android Auto rolls
out to many countries.

00:26:01.100 --> 00:26:04.000
And there are many different
locales, regulations, but also

00:26:04.000 --> 00:26:06.650
driving habits-- left side,
