to be taken into account.

00:26:09.130 --> 00:26:11.100
So when you look at
this overall complexity,

00:26:11.100 --> 00:26:14.420
it's actually a pretty
multi-dimensional problem,

00:26:14.420 --> 00:26:17.240
where on one side you have
an ecosystem of all apps

00:26:17.240 --> 00:26:19.690
