to get on Android Auto.

00:26:19.690 --> 00:26:22.170
On the other side, you have
many different cars and form

00:26:22.170 --> 00:26:22.677
factors.

00:26:22.677 --> 00:26:25.010
And in the middle, you have
many different locales where

00:26:25.010 --> 00:26:26.700
these products will be used.

00:26:26.700 --> 00:26:27.890
That's hard, right?

00:26:27.890 --> 00:26:29.940
But the good news is,
